></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104khr1665702719725.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/khr1665702719725.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/khr1665702719725.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"khr1665702719725\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Allow the select cache mechanism when moving to the last occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"khr1665702719725__topic_d140267e1_d140268e1_d140269e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"khr1665702719725__p_d140270e1_d140271e1_d140272e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"khr1665702719725__section_b1b_4lq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d572674e59\"> Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"khr1665702719725__table_d16874e1_d16875e1_d16876e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> application assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> [SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"khr1665702719725__section_elg_4lq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d572674e105\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"khr1665702719725__p_d140279e1_d140280e1_d140281e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS</span> is\n        present, each occurrence is retrieved into the select cache when moving to the last\n        occurrence, for example, when using the structure editor function ^LAST_OCC or the\n        ProcScript statement <code class=\"ph codeph\">setocc \"*\", -1</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"khr1665702719725__p_d140282e1_d140283e1_d140284e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS</span> is not\n        present, the select cache is not used when moving to the last occurrence. This improves\n        performance when information concerning other records is not required.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"khr1665702719725__section_uqk_4lq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle exampletitle\" id=\"khr1665702719725__p_d140285e1_d140286e1_d140287e1\"> Example:\n        $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"khr1665702719725__pre_p3q_cmq_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udq1665702663280.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Retrieval Processing</a><p>Data is retrieved from the database when the user enters a retrieve profile (that is, a search string) in the desired fields and then enters ^RETRIEVE. Alternatively, ProcScript can be used to assign retrieve profiles to the desired fields in a component. When retrieving data from the database, Uniface selects the required data with the Select connector request, and fetches it into the component with the Fetch connector request.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Allow the select cache mechanism when moving to the last occurrence. $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS Defaults Assignment file: application assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description When $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS is present, each occurrence is retrieved into the select cache when moving to the last occurrence, for example, when using the structure editor function ^LAST_OCC or the ProcScript statement setocc \"*\", -1 . When $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS is not present, the select cache is not used when moving to the last occurrence. This improves performance when information concerning other records is not required. Example: $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS $ENABLE_CACHE_ALWAYS Copy Related Links Retrieval Processing Data is retrieved from the database when the user enters a retrieve profile (that is, a search string) in the desired fields and then enters ^RETRIEVE. Alternatively, ProcScript can be used to assign retrieve profiles to the desired fields in a component. When retrieving data from the database, Uniface selects the required data with the Select connector request, and fetches it into the component with the Fetch connector request. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}